water on the landscape

00:36:58.260 --> 00:37:00.450 align:middle line:84%
by constructing
extremely elaborate dams.

00:37:00.450 --> 00:37:02.580 align:middle line:84%
I have beavers living
in the backyard here.

00:37:02.580 --> 00:37:05.190 align:middle line:84%
And it's not just that
they pile sticks up.

00:37:05.190 --> 00:37:07.710 align:middle line:84%
They excavate mud
and stones, which

00:37:07.710 --> 00:37:09.165 align:middle line:90%
they use in their construction.

00:37:09.165 --> 00:37:11.790 align:middle line:84%
If you go out and pulled-- made
a hole in the dam, the next day

00:37:11.790 --> 00:37:13.780 align:middle line:90%
