00:37:13.780 --> 00:37:20.630 align:middle line:84%
They are incredibly studious
about their environment.

00:37:20.630 --> 00:37:21.840 align:middle line:90%
This is a rodent, right?

00:37:21.840 --> 00:37:24.720 align:middle line:84%
And they know how to
construct dams to hold water

00:37:24.720 --> 00:37:26.583 align:middle line:90%
to create wetland habitats.

00:37:26.583 --> 00:37:28.500 align:middle line:84%
And when we watch what
they do, it's like, oh,

00:37:28.500 --> 00:37:30.840 align:middle line:84%
they create more
species diversity.

00:37:30.840 --> 00:37:34.410 align:middle line:84%
They create more edge habitat,
