like 15,000 years taking

00:41:13.660 --> 00:41:14.460 align:middle line:90%
care of this place.

00:41:14.460 --> 00:41:16.730 align:middle line:84%
And Europeans came over
here and just mowed it down

00:41:16.730 --> 00:41:17.990 align:middle line:90%
in a couple of centuries.

00:41:17.990 --> 00:41:18.883 align:middle line:90%
It's incredible.

00:41:18.883 --> 00:41:20.300 align:middle line:84%
But we ate through
the food chain.

00:41:20.300 --> 00:41:23.060 align:middle line:84%
So we started off
with the big stuff--

00:41:23.060 --> 00:41:26.210 align:middle line:84%
sperm whales, cod,
stuff like that.

00:41:26.210 --> 00:41:29.000 align:middle line:84%
Now, we're getting down to where
