00:41:45.100 --> 00:41:48.500 align:middle line:84%
So domestication has
turned us into a mirror

00:41:48.500 --> 00:41:50.870 align:middle line:90%
image of our nature.

00:41:50.870 --> 00:41:55.430 align:middle line:84%
It's like we are the what you'd
call, like a photo negative.

00:41:55.430 --> 00:41:58.590 align:middle line:84%
We're like the dark version
of what we should be.

